com.bergerkiller.bukkit.common.wrappers

Class PlayerAbilities

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.bergerkiller.bukkit.common.wrappers.BasicWrapper<PlayerAbilitiesHandle>
      • com.bergerkiller.bukkit.common.wrappers.PlayerAbilities

  • public class PlayerAbilities
extends BasicWrapper<PlayerAbilitiesHandle>
    Player abilities wrapper class. Note that Bukkit already provides methods to change these abilities for Players. This wrapper class is intended for human entities or non-player-bound processing.
